notation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","title":"MLNAnnotation","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNVectorStyleLayer/predicate":{"abstract":[{"text":"The style layer’s predicate.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNVectorStyleLayer\/predicate","title":"predicate","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"predicate"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnvectorstylelayer\/predicate","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMultiPolyline":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object represents a shape consisting of one or more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"polylines. For example, you could use a multipolyline shape to represent both","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"sides of a divided highway (dual carriageway), excluding the median (central","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"reservation): each carriageway would be a distinct ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolyline","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" object.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipolyline","title":"MLNMultiPolyline","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMultiPolyline","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNPointCollectionFeature":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpointcollectionfeature","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"MLNPointCollectionFeature","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"MLNPointCollectionFeature","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointCollectionFeature","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object associates a point collection with an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"optional identifier and attributes."}],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointCollectionFeature"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNVectorTileSource":{"abstract":[{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNVectorTileSource","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" is a map content source that supplies tiled vector data","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"in ","type":"text"},{"text":"Mapbox Vector Tile","type":"text"},{"text":" format","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"to be shown on the map. The location of and metadata about the tiles are"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"defined either by an option dictionary or by an external file that conforms to","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"TileJSON specification"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"A vector tile source is added to an "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" object along with one or more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNVectorStyleLayer","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" objects. A vector style layer defines the appearance of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"any content supplied by the vector tile source."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNVectorTileSource","title":"MLNVectorTileSource","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNVectorTileSource"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnvectortilesource","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"role":"collection","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","kind":"symbol","title":"MapLibre","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNPointCollection":{"role":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"MLNPointCollection","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointCollection","kind":"symbol","title":"MLNPointCollection","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointCollection","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" object represents a shape consisting of one or more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"disconnected vertices, specified as "},{"code":"CLLocationCoordinate2D","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" instances. The"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"points in the collection may be related but are not connected spatially. For"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"example, you could use a point collection to represent all the trees in an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"orchard."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpointcollection"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNShapeCollection":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeCollection","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeCollection"},{"type":"text","text":" object represents a shape consisting of zero or more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"distinct but related shapes that are instances of "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape"},{"type":"text","text":". The constituent"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"shapes can be a mixture of different kinds of shapes."}],"kind":"symbol","title":"MLNShapeCollection","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnshapecollection","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNShapeCollection"}],"type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/objc(cs)NSObject":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/objc(cs)NSObject","title":"NSObject","type":"unresolvable"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMultiPolygon":{"type":"topic","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolygon","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object represents a shape consisting of one or more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"polygons that do not overlap. For example, you could use a multipolygon shape"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to represent the body of land that consists of an island surrounded by an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"atoll: the inner island would be one "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolygon","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object, while the surrounding"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"atoll would be another. You could also use a multipolygon shape to represent a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"group of disconnected but related buildings."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipolygon","title":"MLNMultiPolygon","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMultiPolygon","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolygon"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNVectorStyleLayer":{"role":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNVectorStyleLayer"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNVectorStyleLayer","kind":"symbol","title":"MLNVectorStyleLayer","abstract":[{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNVectorStyleLayer","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" is an abstract superclass for style layers whose content","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"is defined by an ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" or ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" object.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnvectorstylelayer"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNShape/geoJSONDataUsingEncoding:":{"role":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"geoJSONDataUsingEncoding:"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape\/geoJSONDataUsingEncoding:","kind":"symbol","title":"geoJSONDataUsingEncoding:","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns the GeoJSON string representation of the shape encapsulated in a data"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnshape\/geojsondatausingencoding:"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNPointAnnotation":{"type":"topic","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointAnnotation","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" object represents a one-dimensional shape located at a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"single geographical coordinate. Depending on how it is used, an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointAnnotation","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" object is known as a point annotation or point shape. For"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"example, you could use a point shape to represent a city at low zoom levels, an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"address at high zoom levels, or the location of a long press gesture."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpointannotation","title":"MLNPointAnnotation","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNPointAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointAnnotation"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNFeature":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNFeature","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":"  protocol is used to provide details about geographic features"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"contained in an "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNVectorTileSource","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" object. Each concrete"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"subclass of "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" in turn has a subclass that conforms to this protocol. A"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"feature object associates a shape with an optional identifier and attributes."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNFeature","title":"MLNFeature","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNFeature"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnfeature","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNShape":{"abstract":[{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" is an abstract class that represents a shape or annotation. Shapes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"constitute the content of a map — not only the overlays atop the map, but also"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the content that forms the base map."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","title":"MLNShape","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNShape"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnshape","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNEmptyFeature":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNEmptyFeature","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNEmptyFeature"},{"type":"text","text":" object associates an empty shape with an optional"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"identifier and attributes."}],"kind":"symbol","title":"MLNEmptyFeature","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnemptyfeature","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNEmptyFeature"}],"type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNShape/subtitle":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnshape\/subtitle","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"subtitle","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"subtitle","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The subtitle of the shape annotation. The default value of this property is"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape\/subtitle"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNStyle":{"type":"topic","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The proxy object for the current map style."}],"kind":"symbol","title":"MLNStyle","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnstyle","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNStyle"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNPolygon":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolygon","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" object represents a closed shape consisting of four or more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"vertices, specified as "},{"code":"CLLocationCoordinate2D","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" instances, and the edges that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"connect them. For example, you could use a polygon shape to represent a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"building, a lake, or an area you want to highlight."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolygon","title":"MLNPolygon","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNPolygon"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpolygon","type":"topic"}}}